Gerrresheimer Raises 2011 Sales Goal on ‘Strong Burst of Growth’

-- B y   A n g e l a   C u l l e n
-- 
2011-10-06T05:34:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/gerrresheimer-raises-2011-sales-goal-on-strong-burst-of-growth-.html
Gerresheimer AG (GXI)  increased its sales
forecast for the year after a “strong burst of growth” in the
third quarter. It now expects sales to rise as much as eight
percent compared with a previous target of as much as seven
percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  